column5: The aim of the game is to through heaven and hell to find oneself after waking up in an unknown forest lost and befuddled. To find oneself one must become Baryonic Person (short Bary), which is shown as an ARC19 NFT with 60 bodyparts in 60 chemical elements.
column10: Levels contain storybits, puzzles, scenery, factoids and desiciions.
column16: Every HMP NFT on purchase contains an amount of $Mori.
column17: $Mori is used to buy Bary body parts, bribe puzzle gate keepers.
column18: Every level is an opportinity to gain a Baryonic Person body part by picking a random number from 1-60. If same layer is entered more than once, the player can pick a number for Bary again.
column19: Every level has different chances for each element based on levels storypart and scene location.
column21: Game is won when Baryonic Person is complete and all 100 levels has been entered.
